          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日里贪酒色不理朝纲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼见得这江山付于汪洋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身在胧朦睡，怀揣社稷忧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官田单，齐王驾前为臣，官拜巡城御史。适才家院报道，东宫小千岁，连夜"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "逃出皇城，不知为了何事。因此下官亲自巡查。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二衙役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二衙役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫人来掌红灯大街来上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "若有那面生人细问端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（田法章上。二衙役同拿田法章。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二衙役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿住了犯夜的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计你看住他，我去讨赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，我来看住他，你去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回禀老爷的话，小人拿住犯夜的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你拿着犯夜的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，回衙有赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢老爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有了赏了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看住他，我也去弄一份。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回禀老爷的话，我也拿着犯夜的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你也拿着犯夜的了？也有赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也有了赏了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看住他，我再去弄一份！"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回禀老爷的话，小人又拿着犯夜的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽，夜静更深，哪有许多犯夜之人？掌灯，老爷亲自观看！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（衙役甲允。田单看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "田法章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，卿……"
        },
        {
          "character": "田单",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "静声！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（田单踢灯，扯田法章同下。二衙役同摸灯。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿……"
        },
        {
          "character": "衙役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "静声！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（衙役甲扯衙役乙同下。）"
        }
      ],
